name: “Inception”
description:
The bodily life is nothing more than the preparation of the soul for eternal life. In it we can only believe and dream. Dream of pure, immaculate. This work is a fantasy about the borderline state of our dreams, our soul. They are always high, somewhere near the clouds, but they were born and rest on the ground, sometimes on lifeless. Light, pure, eternal can arise on the ashes.

.2021
